playstore_details.description:
Get fit and shed pounds with E-Pedometer! 

🔋 Accurate & Battery-Saving 
Auto track steps without GPS, sign-in, or Wi-Fi. Minimal battery consumption with built-in sensor usage.

🏃‍♂️ Easy-to-Use 
Free pedometer with automatic start and stop. Works accurately in pocket or bag.

🔒 Free & Private 
No sign-in needed. We prioritize your privacy—no data collection or sharing.

📊 Report Graphs 
Visualize steps, distance, time, and calories daily, weekly, and monthly.

🎯 Set Personal Goals 
Tailor daily goals based on age, weight, etc. Monitor progress with run tracker and graphs.

🏋️‍♀️ Health & Fitness 
Reliable Android pedometer for daily health monitoring. Compatible with all Android devices.

Download now for step, calorie, distance, and run tracking. Walk towards better health effortlessly. 

Thanks for using E-Pedometer: Step Tracker! ❤️
